      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Pyrokinesis</em></p>\n<p>A line of roaring Force-enhanced flame 30 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in the line must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 3d8]] energy damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Force Potency.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a force slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
